  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_000&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほら、早く顔を洗って</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Have you washed your face?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトが実は『音』の精霊だって
わかったけど、</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We know that Eto is the
Spirit of Sound, yet... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>とりあえず、わたしたちが
独り立ちできるまで一緒に
暮らすことになりました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Until we can make a living,
we're all living together like 
always.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Tl check </Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……もちろん、
&lt;Couleur&gt;も一緒ですよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, yeah. &lt;Couleur&gt; is
here, too. I guess?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305316</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊の力はそれぞれの
精霊の元へ戻って</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've returned the power of the
Spirits to where they belong.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305316</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エレメンツポットは、
今では思い出です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Elements' Pot is little
more than a memento now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……あれから、
もうだいぶなるよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Things are starting to look up again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね……
みんな、元気かな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes. Everyone looks so happy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おっはよー！
元気してる！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hello~! Anyone alive inside?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……&lt;Arche&gt;さんは
元気みたいだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Looks like Miss &lt;Arche&gt;
is doing just fine.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何しに来たの、
&lt;Arche&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What brings you here, &lt;Arche&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>暇だから
遊びに来ただけよ。
何さ、悪い？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I had some free time, so I thought
I'd stop by and have some fun.
Is it a problem?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレら、
仕事で忙しいの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We're all busy with work, y' know!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306176</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>休みなさいって。
今日一日くらい、
このあたしが許す！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then take a break! Today is your
monthly break! I'll allow it~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いい気なものだ。
自分の罪を一切知らず</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How cute. They act as if
they have no sins to bear.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>幸せな姿を見ていると、
塵一つ残さず、壊したくなる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If this uniformity is the happiness you seek,
then it is one begging to be destroyed.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306652</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえら……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306712</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うわっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_250_030_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>待てっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hang on!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
